Description

Join Crazy Frog and a brand new bunch of his friends (and enemies!) in his very first videogame - CRAZY FROG RACER! Race kart style around twelve of the most amazingly crazy tracks using some of the most crazzzzy power ups known to frog! He makes crazy noises, he goes crazily fast, and he wants you to have some crazy fun! As well as the Annoying Thing, meet Ellie the Fairy, Ninja Gorilla, Mad French Chef, Geerty the Cow, the Gangsta kids, and many many more!
